<plot>Enhanced media coverage of the War in Iraq is leading to wide-spread Media censorship. High Ranking Military leaders are using Military Public Affairs, an organization in charge of Media on the Battlefield, in order to control information in Iraq. This film tells the story of one Public Affairs Soldier's experience in Iraq and the media censorship that he saw and was a part of.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268355</url></doc>
